"Overhead rectangular:      Isometric rectangular:\n"
"      _________               /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"                             \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"Hex:                       Iso-hex:\n"
"  /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\               _   _   _   _   _\n"
"  | | | | | | |             / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
"  \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\             \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/\n"
"   | | | | | | |            / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
